{
  "stem": "7506.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I don't recall anything towards me personally.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And for that matter, I recall very little of his behavior, for example, towards my father or mother, certainly in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As the time progressed, sometimes I recall-- sometimes that come, I don't know what you call it in English.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I really don't know what you call it in English.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But in Dutch it's called [SPEAKING DUTCH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it's a can.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's like a can where farmers would put the milk in, would come into the camp, in our part of the camp, with milk.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I would-- everybody would be clamoring for a little bit of milk.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I can remember on various occasions going there for milk for my sister, and it being refused to me by a Dutch Jewish man.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The Dutch Jewish man, his name-- I don't know if he's still alive.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "His name was Ben Brill.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Brill is B-R-I-L-L.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he was before the war a boxer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was well-known in Holland in those days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He survived the war.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I always remember going, trying to force my way through the people to try and get a little bit of milk for my sister.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I dare say, looking at it now, you know, so many years after the event, I would say probably there was none left.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I think at the time, I took it as an affront to me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I took it as an affront.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe I didn't realize quite that it was gone, you know, that it was finished.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because there'd be only a little amount that would come into the camp, and not very often at that.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
